milestones.description: Burmester and Andy Flower's 104-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 92 between Campbell and Andy Flower
Zimbabwe's 75-run win against Pakistan is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 13-run win against Australia
Moin Khan has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (5) in ODIs for PAK, going past Wasim Bari's 4
